随着[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]逐步升级，战斗也从[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]蔓延到了[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]。黎巴嫩境内的支持和反对叙利亚政府的派别中都有成员来到叙利亚参与内战。而在黎巴嫩境内，双方也发生了冲突。

叙利亚内战也被认为煽动了黎巴嫩境内的宗派冲突<ref name=holmes>{{cite news|last=Holmes|first=Oliver|title=Bombs kill 42 outside mosques in Lebanon's Tripoli|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/08/23/us-lebanon-explosion-deaths-idUSBRE97M0FL20130823|accessdate=2013-08-30|agency=Reuters|date=2013-08-23|archive-date=2013-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130829190411/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/08/23/us-lebanon-explosion-deaths-idUSBRE97M0FL20130823|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，因为黎巴嫩的逊尼派大多支持叙利亚反对派武装。而[[什叶派|什叶派]]大多支持阿萨德政府，因为[[巴沙尔·阿萨德|巴沙尔·阿萨德]]属于阿拉维派，该教派通常被认为是什叶派的分支<ref name=bassam>{{cite news|last=Bassam|first=Laila|title=Car bomb kills 20 in Hezbollah's Beirut stronghold|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/08/15/us-lebanon-explosion-idUSBRE97E0S520130815|accessdate=2013-08-30|agency=Reuters|date=2013-08-15|archive-date=2013-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130825225334/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/08/15/us-lebanon-explosion-idUSBRE97E0S520130815|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在黎巴嫩全境，针对外国人的谋杀、骚乱和绑架时有发生。

在2011年中旬在[[的黎波里_(黎巴嫩)|的黎波里]]的一次冲突中，共有7人丧生、59人受伤。2012年3月冲突蔓延到了[[贝鲁特|贝鲁特]]，之后蔓延到了黎巴嫩南部和东部，而政府军被部署到了黎巴嫩北部和贝鲁特。截止2013年12月至少有355人在冲突中丧生、超过2,000人受伤。

在黎巴嫩政治格局中。由[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]支持的“[[三月十四日聯盟|三月十四日聯盟]]”（March 14 Alliance）支持叙利亚反对派，而[[伊朗|伊朗]]支持的“[[三月八日联盟|三月八日联盟]]”支持叙利亚政府。

==背景==

自从2005年[[雪松革命|雪松革命]]及叙利亚军队从黎巴嫩撤离之后，黎巴嫩政治格局被分化为支持叙利亚政府的“3月8日联盟”以及反对叙利亚政府的“3月14日联盟”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=367808|title=Jumblatt joins anti-Syrian regime protest in Beirut|newspaper=NOW Lebanon|date=2012-02-22|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320044304/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=367808|archive-date=2012-03-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。“3月14日联盟”由逊尼派为主要组成部分的未来阵线领导，并且与[[马龙派|基督教马龙派]]组成的[[黎巴嫩长枪党|黎巴嫩长枪党]]结盟。该政治联盟呼吁黎巴嫩支持[[叙利亚自由军|叙利亚自由军]]并且对叙利亚政府持更加强硬的立场<ref>{{cite news|url=http://dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Oct-09/190673-syria-conflict-causing-tension-between-sleiman-hezbollah.ashx#axzz28wXupzcR|title=Syria conflict causing tension|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2012-09-10|accessdate=2012-09-10|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116092830/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Oct-09/190673-syria-conflict-causing-tension-between-sleiman-hezbollah.ashx#axzz28wXupzcR|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.economist.com/blogs/democracyinamerica/2012/10/violence|title=Violence: Who says America doesn't have castles?|newspaper=The Economist|date=2012-10-24|accessdate=2012-11-27|journal=|archive-date=2012-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109174458/http://www.economist.com/blogs/democracyinamerica/2012/10/violence|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这一呼吁被占主导地位的“3月8日联盟”所拒绝。该联盟包括黎巴嫩真主党以及与其结盟的隶属于基督教马龙派的自由爱国党及其他一些政党。

黎巴嫩未来阵线领导人Okab Sakr被怀疑卷入到支持叙利亚反对派的活动<ref>{{cite news|url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/exclusive-inside-future-movements-syria-arms-trade|title=Exclusive: Inside Future Movement's Syria Arms Trade|newspaper=Al Akhbar|date=2012-11-29|accessdate=2012-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140402175344/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/exclusive-inside-future-movements-syria-arms-trade|archive-date=2014-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/62811-syrian-armed-opposition-leader-asks-saqr-for-arms-in-leaked-audio-tape|title='Syrian Armed Opposition Leader' Asks Saqr for Arms in Leaked Audio Tape|newspaper=Naharnet|date=2012-11-29|accessdate=2012-12-24|archive-date=2019-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511144636/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/62811-syrian-armed-opposition-leader-asks-saqr-for-arms-in-leaked-audio-tape|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在起初他否认了这一指责，但在黎巴嫩《Al Akbhar》报公开了录有他与叙利亚反对派进行武器交易的录音带后他承认他卷入了支持叙利亚反对派的活动<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/63099-saqr-confirms-leaked-audio-recording-on-arms-deal-says-ready-to-lift-off-his-immunity|title=Saqr Confirms Leaked Audio Recording on Arms Deal, Says Ready to Lift Off his Immunity|newspaper=Naharnet|date=2012-12-03|accessdate=2012-12-24|archive-date=2019-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511144638/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/63099-saqr-confirms-leaked-audio-recording-on-arms-deal-says-ready-to-lift-off-his-immunity|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Okab Sakr之后声称录音带是经过剪辑的，他只向叙利亚方面提供了牛奶和毛毯<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/63552-saqr-challenges-foes-to-prove-involvement-in-arms-trade-as-he-broadcasts-original-tapes|title=Saqr Challenges Foes to Prove Involvement in Arms Trade as he Broadcasts Original Tapes|newspaper=Naharnet|date=2012-12-06|accessdate=2012-12-24|archive-date=2019-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511144636/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/63552-saqr-challenges-foes-to-prove-involvement-in-arms-trade-as-he-broadcasts-original-tapes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

来自的黎波里的逊尼派极端分子中有很多人前往叙利亚加入了恐怖组织[[努斯拉阵线|努斯拉阵线]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/closer-ties-emerge-between-sunni-militants-from-lebanon-and-syria-officials-say/2013/01/26/451f0bec-66f9-11e2-9e1b-07db1d2ccd5b_print.html |title=closer-ties-emerge-between-sunni-militants-from-lebanon-and-syria-officials-say More Lebanese Sunnis are crossing into Syria to aid rebellion, officials say |work=The Washington Post |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814213646/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/closer-ties-emerge-between-sunni-militants-from-lebanon-and-syria-officials-say/2013/01/26/451f0bec-66f9-11e2-9e1b-07db1d2ccd5b_print.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而真主党武装分子则進駐叙黎边境居住着什叶派群众的城镇，保衛它們免遭叙利亚反对派的袭击。黎巴嫩政府军则避免卷入到叙利亚内战当中，并阻止黎巴嫩境内发生冲突<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/67634 |title=Report: Hizbullah Training Shiite Syrians to Defend Villages against Rebels |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2019-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511144640/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/67634 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==时间表==

===早期冲突===
[[File:Lebanese_army_on_Syria_Street.jpg|thumb]]
2011年6月17日冲突在一个支持叙利亚政府的游行之后爆发。战斗双方分别为来自敌对社区的武装分子。一伙武装分子来自贾巴穆森（Jabal Mohsen），这个社区的居民主要是支持叙利亚政府的阿拉维派。而另一伙武装分子来自巴布艾特巴尼（Bab al-Tabbaneh），该社区居民主要以逊尼派为主，支持叙利亚反对派。冲突共导致7人丧生、59人受伤。死者中包括一名黎巴嫩政府军士兵和一名来自由阿拉维派组成的阿拉伯民主党官员。

2012年2月10日至11日在贾巴穆森和巴布艾特巴尼的冲突导致2到3人丧生。而政府军随后介入了冲突，又导致6名士兵受伤<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/16/world/middleeast/syrias-unrest-felt-by-military-in-lebanon.html|work=The New York Times|first=Josh|last=Wood|title=Syria's Unrest Felt by Military in Lebanon|date=2012-02-15|accessdate=2014-03-02|archive-date=2014-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028082144/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/16/world/middleeast/syrias-unrest-felt-by-military-in-lebanon.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/02/2012211233556510327.html|title=Syrian violence spills over into Lebanon|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=2012-02-11|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002212809/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/02/2012211233556510327.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年4月29日黎巴嫩海军在“Lutfallah II”号集装箱船中查获大批武器弹药。在被黎巴嫩海军阻截之前，这艘船整驶向黎巴嫩北部的[[的黎波里_(黎巴嫩)|的黎波里]]港。这艘船是从[[利比亚|利比亚]]起航，而在被查获的弹药中很多都来自利比亚。根据[[BBC|BBC]]的报道，据信这批军火是运给叙利亚反对派的<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-17885085|title=Lebanon holds ship 'carrying weapons for Syria rebels'|publisher=BBC|date=2012-04-29|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2012-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120822144322/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-17885085|dead-url=no}}</ref>据报道有4人在叙利亚反对派的支持者与来自"Tawheed运动"的逊尼派叙利亚政府支持者之间的冲突中受伤。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Apr-24/171237-plumbly-visits-tripoli-says-concerned-over-security-situation.ashx#axzz1vVVwqM3z|title=Plumbly praises Tripoli authorities for restoring calm following Sunday unrest|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2012-04-24|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-date=2017-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107014419/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Apr-24/171237-plumbly-visits-tripoli-says-concerned-over-security-situation.ashx#axzz1vVVwqM3z|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===2012年5月巴布艾特巴尼—贾巴穆森冲突===
2012年5月在的黎波里的萨拉菲主义者要求释放逊尼派伊斯兰教主义者Shadi Mawlawi，此人因为被控是一个恐怖组织成员而被捕。萨拉菲主义者声称如果政府军试图用武力清除他们设立的路障，他们就准备战斗到底<ref name="spillover_to_lebaonon">[http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=396254 Death toll in Lebanon’s Tripoli rises amid sectarian clashes] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120906161702/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=396254 |date=2012-09-06 }} NOW lebanon, 14 May 2012</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-12/173188-safadi-ask-for-release-of-tripoli-man-tricked-by-general-security.ashx#axzz1vVVwqM3z|title=Safadi asks for release of Tripoli man tricked by General Security|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2012-05-12|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608034215/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-12/173188-safadi-ask-for-release-of-tripoli-man-tricked-by-general-security.ashx#axzz1vVVwqM3z|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

逮捕Shadi Mawlawi的举动引发了的黎波里的伊斯兰主义者与阿拉维派之间新一轮的冲突<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/May-19/173918-signs-point-to-mawlawi-release-next-week-tripoli-truce-holds.ashx#axzz1wfAAqBXx|title=Signs point to Mawlawi release next week, Tripoli truce holds|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2012-05-19|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604095600/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/May-19/173918-signs-point-to-mawlawi-release-next-week-tripoli-truce-holds.ashx#axzz1wfAAqBXx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=395639|title=Hariri condemns Tripoli clashes|newspaper=NOW Lebanon|date=2012-05-13|accessdate=2012-05-25|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306153014/https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/archive/hariri_condemns_tripoli_clashes_caused_by_mawlawis_arrest1|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。大约2到4人在5月12日夜里的冲突中丧生。战斗发生在一块被逊尼派聚居区包围的阿拉维派聚居区及其周边的逊尼派社区。在那场战斗中，双方使用了火箭弹和自动步枪。在冲突爆发前数小时，黎巴嫩政府军与一群年轻的伊斯兰主义者发生交火。当时这群人正在的黎波里举行抗议活动，要求释放一名恐怖分子嫌疑人。冲突是由于当时这群同情叙利亚反对派的年轻人正试图闯入亲叙利亚政府的叙利亚社会民主党的办公室。 据报道，在死者中有3名是逊尼派平民，一名为政府军军官。

冲突持续到了5月14日，最后总共导致5名阿拉维派和1名逊尼派丧生<ref name="naharnet1">{{cite news|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/40122-tripoli-sectarian-violence-toll-rises-to-4-amid-intermittent-clashes|title=6 Dead, 70 Hurt as Clashes Spread in Tripoli and Islamists Reclose al-Nour Square|newspaper=Naharnet|date=2012-05-14|accessdate=2012-12-25|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603174657/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/40122-tripoli-sectarian-violence-toll-rises-to-4-amid-intermittent-clashes|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="dailystar1">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-14/173316-1-killed-10-wounded-in-renewed-fighting-in-north-lebanon.ashx#axzz1uhec4y59|title=North Lebanon clashes escalate, kill 5|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2012-05-14|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116091343/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-14/173316-1-killed-10-wounded-in-renewed-fighting-in-north-lebanon.ashx#axzz1uhec4y59|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月15日政府军被部署到这一地区并介入到冲突中，导致8人受伤，其中包括1名政府军士兵<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-16/173584-4-wounded-in-clashes-between-army-gunmen.ashx#axzz1uzBSxwRs|title=Lebanese soldier among 8 wounded in north Lebanon clashes|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2012-05-16|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604015034/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-16/173584-4-wounded-in-clashes-between-army-gunmen.ashx#axzz1uzBSxwRs|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截止5月16日，冲突导致11人丧生，其中包括1名士兵<ref name="naharnet1"/><ref name="dailystar1"/><ref name="al-akhbar1">{{cite news|url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/clashes-resume-tripoli-several-wounded|title=Clashes resume in Tripoli, several wounded|newspaper=Al Akhbar|date=2012-05-16|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019114254/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/clashes-resume-tripoli-several-wounded|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而截至5月18日，在冲突中总共有12人丧生，超过100人受伤<ref name="yalibnan1">{{cite news|url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/05/18/geagea-hezbollah-training-arming-tripoli-groups/#more-39409|title=Geagea: Hezbollah training, arming Tripoli groups|newspaper=Ya Libnan|date=2012-05-18|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2012-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120520140539/http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/05/18/geagea-hezbollah-training-arming-tripoli-groups/#more-39409|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="naharnet1"/><ref name="dailystar1"/>。

===艾哈迈德 阿布德-瓦希德遇害事件===

2012年5月20日著名黎巴嫩逊尼派神职人员沙伊赫·艾哈迈德·阿布德-瓦希德（Sheikh Ahmad Abdel-Wahid）及其助手Mohammed Merheb被黎巴嫩政府军射杀。当时他们没有及时在Akkar的一处政府军检查站前及时停下<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/05/20/215273.html|title=Army kills Sunni cleric in Lebanon: security official|publisher=Al Arabiya|date=2012-05-20|accessdate=2012-08-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120630053830/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/05/20/215273.html|archivedate=2012-06-30}}</ref>。他的死引发了抗议活动，这些抗议者在全国很多地方用燃烧的轮胎阻断了很多道路。一名逊尼派领导人威胁人如果当局不着手解决这起谋杀事件，他将组建一支“黎巴嫩自由军”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=398665|title=Akkar sheikhs threaten to establishing Free Lebanese Army?|publisher=NOW Lebanon|date=2012-05-20|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120522101430/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=398665|archive-date=2012-05-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在之后的几天，22名当时在枪击现场的政府军士兵被捕，而未来阵线领导人Khaled Al Daher要求处死他们<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/40951-tense-funeral-for-abdul-wahed-merheb-in-al-bireh-daher-calls-for-executing-killers|title=Tense Funeral for Abdul Wahed, Merheb in al-Bireh, Daher Calls for Executing Killers|publisher=Naharnet|date=2012-05-21|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603174658/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/40951-tense-funeral-for-abdul-wahed-merheb-in-al-bireh-daher-calls-for-executing-killers|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

5月22日逊尼派伊斯兰教主义者Shadi Mawlawi在的黎波里获释<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-22/174264-lebanese-judge-approves-mawlawis-release-on-bail.ashx#axzz1wfAAqBXx|title=Mawlawi, newly freed: I confessed under duress|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-05-22|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605043113/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-22/174264-lebanese-judge-approves-mawlawis-release-on-bail.ashx#axzz1wfAAqBXx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

5月24日反对叙利亚政府的“3月14日联盟”呼吁政府关注那些“试图毁灭黎巴嫩的企图”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/41319-march-14-for-a-neutral-salvation-govt-that-would-launch-dialogue-on-all-illegal-arms|title=March 14: For a Neutral, Salvation Govt. that would Launch Dialogue on All Illegal Arms|publisher=Naharnet|date=2012-05-24|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-date=2012-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527084644/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/41319-march-14-for-a-neutral-salvation-govt-that-would-launch-dialogue-on-all-illegal-arms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。与此同时在的黎波里，伊斯兰主义者在抗议活动中威胁如果政府不释放那些因为参与2007年黎巴嫩武装冲突而被捕并受到指控的大约180名伊斯兰主义者，他们的示威活动将蔓延到黎巴嫩全境<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/May-25/174677-protesters-threaten-to-expand-north-lebanon-demos.ashx#axzz1vVVwqM3z|title=Protesters threaten to expand north Lebanon demos|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-05-25|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609002702/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/May-25/174677-protesters-threaten-to-expand-north-lebanon-demos.ashx#axzz1vVVwqM3z|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

5月28日一名平民因为没有在一处政府军检查站前及时停下而被政府军射杀<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-28/174825-soldiers-kill-man-who-refuses-to-stop-at-batroun-checkpoint.ashx#axzz1wAISkDxl|title=Soldiers kill man who refuses to stop at Batroun checkpoint|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-05-28|accessdate=2012-08-23|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924015136/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-28/174825-soldiers-kill-man-who-refuses-to-stop-at-batroun-checkpoint.ashx#axzz1wAISkDxl|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===贝鲁特冲突===
