9月6日在贝鲁特，未来阵线的成员与部署到当地的政府军发生枪战，2人受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/52645-two-wounded-in-tariq-al-jadideh-clash-as-army-deploys-to-contain-situation|title=Two Hurt as Families Dispute Erupts into Armed Clash in Tariq al-Jadideh|publisher=Naharnet|date=2012-09-06|accessdate=2012-10-20|archive-date=2019-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607180813/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/52645-two-wounded-in-tariq-al-jadideh-clash-as-army-deploys-to-contain-situation|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===绑架事件===
2012年5月叙利亚反对派在叙黎边境的Zeita村附近绑架了3名亲叙利亚政府的黎巴嫩人。作为报复，60名叙利亚劳工遭到绑架。这些被绑架者在5月16日被交换并获释<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-16/173574-lebanese-syrian-hostages-released-as-part-of-swap-deal.ashx#axzz1vVVwqM3z|title=Lebanese, Syrian hostages released in swap|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-05-16|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2016-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414195923/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-16/173574-lebanese-syrian-hostages-released-as-part-of-swap-deal.ashx#axzz1vVVwqM3z|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

5月22日至少16名黎巴嫩什叶派朝圣者在[[阿勒颇|阿勒颇]]被叙利亚自由军绑架<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-22/174279-12-lebanese-kidnapped-by-free-syrian-army-local-media.ashx#axzz1vVVwqM3z|title=At least 16 Lebanese abducted by Syria rebels near Aleppo|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-05-22|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308024558/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-22/174279-12-lebanese-kidnapped-by-free-syrian-army-local-media.ashx#axzz1vVVwqM3z|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/12-lebanese-kidnapped-free-syrian-army|title=Nasrallah urges calm after Syrian rebels kidnap Lebanese|publisher=Al Akhbar|date=2012-05-22|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120728074727/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/12-lebanese-kidnapped-free-syrian-army|archive-date=2012-07-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[叙利亚自由军|叙利亚自由军]]否认绑架了这些朝圣者，指责绑架者是黑帮成员并声称将帮助这些朝圣者获救<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/41174-free-syrian-army-mafias-kidnapped-lebanese-pilgrims-we-will-risk-our-lives-to-free-them|title=Free Syrian Army: Mafias Kidnapped Lebanese Pilgrims, We Will Risk Our Lives to Free them|publisher=Naharnet|date=2012-05-23|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603040207/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/41174-free-syrian-army-mafias-kidnapped-lebanese-pilgrims-we-will-risk-our-lives-to-free-them|dead-url=no}}</ref>。绑架者声称如果黎巴嫩政府承认叙利亚反对派，他们将释放这些朝圣者<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/49515-kidnapper-of-11-pilgrims-lebanese-politicians-must-recognize-syrian-revolution|title=Kidnapper of 11 Pilgrims: Lebanese Politicians Must Recognize Syrian Revolution|publisher=Naharnet|date=2012-08-09|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2017-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707235412/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/49515-kidnapper-of-11-pilgrims-lebanese-politicians-must-recognize-syrian-revolution|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在这些被绑架的人当中，1人在8月25日获释<ref name="aljazaug"/>。

在5月末两名黎巴嫩农民亲叙利亚的武装分子被绑架并被带往叙利亚。在黎巴嫩阿拉伯民主党的领导人Rifaat Eid的调解下<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jun-02/175494-abducted-lebanon-farmers-to-be-freed-shortly-arab-democratic-party.ashx#axzz1wfAAqBXx|title=Abducted Lebanese farmers to be freed shortly: Arab Democratic Party|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-06-02|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417025316/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jun-02/175494-abducted-lebanon-farmers-to-be-freed-shortly-arab-democratic-party.ashx#axzz1wfAAqBXx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这两人在6月3日获释<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/syria-releases-abducted-lebanese-farmers|title=Syria releases abducted Lebanese farmers|publisher=Al Akhbar|date=2012-06-04|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120606030833/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/syria-releases-abducted-lebanese-farmers|archive-date=2012-06-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

在6月有很多人因为其他的绑架事件而被绑架<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jun-10/176308-north-lebanon-man-kidnapped-in-tit-for-tat-abduction.ashx|title=Three remain captive after revenge kidnapping in north Lebanon|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-06-10|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2012-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120831170048/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jun-10/176308-north-lebanon-man-kidnapped-in-tit-for-tat-abduction.ashx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月25日一名科威特公民在[[贝卡谷地|贝卡谷地]]的Howsh al-Ghanam遭到绑架，但是这件绑架事件被安全部队怀疑有政治目的<ref name="aljazaug">{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/08/2012825104753880245.html|title=Kuwaiti man latest Lebanon kidnap victim|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=2012-08-25|accessdate=2012-10-20|archive-date=2019-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422155228/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/08/2012825104753880245.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===梅克达德绑架事件===
信奉什叶派的梅克达德家族绑架了20人，据称这些人主要是叙利亚自由军成员，但也包括了一名土耳其人。这起绑架事件是作为哈桑·梅克达德在2012年8月13日遭到叙利亚自由军绑架的报复行动。梅克达德家族的武装组织威胁如果哈桑·梅克达德不被释放，他们将采取更多行动<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/08/15/us-syria-crisis-lebanon-abductions-idUSBRE87E0XP20120815|title=Lebanese Shi'ites kidnap 20, Sunni neighbors targeted|agency=Reuters|date=2012-08-15|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2012-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120825232645/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/08/15/us-syria-crisis-lebanon-abductions-idUSBRE87E0XP20120815|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Aug-16/184797-asiri-denies-saudi-kidnapped-in-lebanon.ashx#axzz23YkAAByr|title=Lebanese clan says it has suspended kidnappings|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-08-16|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609082229/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Aug-16/184797-asiri-denies-saudi-kidnapped-in-lebanon.ashx#axzz23YkAAByr|dead-url=no}}</ref>。多名被绑架者因为与叙利亚自由军无关而被释放。梅克达德家族的发言人声称这起绑架是因为黎巴嫩政府没有采取行动以保证他们家族被绑架的成员获释而进行的。作为对绑架以及警告的回应，沙烏地阿拉伯、卡達、土耳其以及其他波斯灣地区阿拉伯国家警告本国公民离开黎巴嫩。黎巴嫩真主党声称政府无力采取行动解救在境外被绑架的黎巴嫩公民，抗议者对此感到愤怒并封锁了街道。这使得黎巴嫩真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉声称针对真主党的抗议活动已经失去了控制。这一声明又在3月14日引发了群众和媒体对真主党的批评。

===6月至7月的黎波里冲突===
2012年5月30日贾巴穆森社区和巴布艾特巴尼社区之间的冲突又造成2人受伤<ref name="dailystar2">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-31/175228-dispute-between-rival-tripoli-residents-wounds-2.ashx#axzz1wAISkDxl|title=Dispute between rival Tripoli residents wounds 2|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-05-31|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203053436/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-31/175228-dispute-between-rival-tripoli-residents-wounds-2.ashx#axzz1wAISkDxl|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

6月2日至3日在的黎波里附近的冲突导致15人丧生，超过60人受伤。作为对这次战斗的回应，政府军重新开进了分隔了交战双方所在的社区的叙利亚大街，并在冲突双方之间设立了缓冲区<ref name="al-akhbar2">{{cite web|url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/tense-calm-returns-tripoli|title=Tense calm returns to Lebanon's Tripoli|publisher=Al Akhbar|date=2012-06-04|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2018-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003020623/https://english.al-akhbar.com/content/tense-calm-returns-tripoli|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="dailystar4">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jun-03/175512-fierce-clashes-rage-in-north-lebanon-12-killed.ashx#axzz1wemAxSeY|title=Cautious calm in north Lebanon marred by sporadic shooting|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-06-03|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116092835/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jun-03/175512-fierce-clashes-rage-in-north-lebanon-12-killed.ashx#axzz1wemAxSeY|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="yalibnan2">{{cite web|url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/06/03/lebanese-army-deployed-in-tripoli-after-15-killed/|title=Lebanese army deployed in Tripoli after 15 killed|publisher=Ya Libnan|date=2012-06-03|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222064943/http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/06/03/lebanese-army-deployed-in-tripoli-after-15-killed/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="aljazeera2">{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/06/201262155357553555.html|title=Lebanon sends troops to quell deadly clashes|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=2012-06-21|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002210313/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/06/201262155357553555.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在冲突双方达成停火之后，在6月2日夜间又发生了多起违反停火的行为，导致1名警察和1名政府军士兵受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/06/03/several-ceasefire-violations-were-reported-in-tripoli/|title=Several ceasefire violations were reported in Tripoli|publisher=Ya Libnan|date=2012-06-03|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604185054/http://yalibnan.com/2012/06/03/several-ceasefire-violations-were-reported-in-tripoli/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

6月8日在的黎波里的阿拉维派社区发生枪战，导致1人丧生、3人受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/lebanese-man-killed-tripoli-gunfire|title=Lebanese man killed in Tripoli gunfire|publisher=Al Akhbar|date=2012-06-08|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120610033320/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/lebanese-man-killed-tripoli-gunfire|archive-date=2012-06-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

6月25日在黎巴嫩北部的Miniyeh，由于支持不同的政治派别，多个家族的成员之间爆发冲突<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jun-25/178075-several-wounded-in-n-lebanon-clash-between-supporters-of-rival-mps.ashx#axzz1y8xjXkuw|title=Several wounded in N. Lebanon clash|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-06-25|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2019-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602200500/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jun-25/178075-several-wounded-in-n-lebanon-clash-between-supporters-of-rival-mps.ashx#axzz1y8xjXkuw|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

7月18日在的黎波里的一场庆祝多名叙利亚部长遭到炸弹袭击的反叙利亚活动中，1人因流弹丧生、多人受伤<ref name="naharnet3">{{cite web|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/47044-one-killed-in-tripoli-by-gunshots-fired-in-celebration-of-damascus-bombing|title=One Killed in Tripoli by Gunshots Fired in Celebration of Damascus Bombing|publisher=Naharnet|date=2012-07-18|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2018-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005210107/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/47044-one-killed-in-tripoli-by-gunshots-fired-in-celebration-of-damascus-bombing|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="al-akhbar3">{{cite web|url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/one-dead-lebanon-after-anti-assad-celebrations|title=One dead in Lebanon after anti-Assad celebrations|publisher=Al Akhbar|date=2012-07-18|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2018-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003013723/https://english.al-akhbar.com/content/one-dead-lebanon-after-anti-assad-celebrations|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

7月27日有两人在返回位于贾巴穆森社区的途中遭到不明身份袭击者的刺死。这起袭击事件引起了武装分子之间的冲突，造成15人受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/48076-fighting-erupts-in-rival-tripoli-districts-army-hits-back-at-shooters|title=Fighting Erupts in Rival Tripoli Districts, Army Hits Back at Shooters|publisher=Naharnet|date=2012-07-27|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2018-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005210039/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/48076-fighting-erupts-in-rival-tripoli-districts-army-hits-back-at-shooters|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===叙黎边境的冲突===

2012年初夏有兩名真主党武装分子在叙利亚境内与反对派交战时被击毙<ref name="increases">{{cite web|url=http://www.northjersey.com/news/international/171434781_Hezbollah_Increases_Support_for_Syrian_Regime__U_S__and_Lebanese_Officials_Say__Beirut_.html|title=Hezbollah Increases Support for Syrian Regime, U.S. and Lebanese Officials Say|publisher=Northjersey.com|date=2012-09-26|accessdate=2012-12-25|archive-date=2020-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200511230903/http://www.northjersey.com/errors/404/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

9月17日叙利亚攻击机对Arsal附近的目标发射了3枚导弹，这3枚导弹越过叙黎边境500余公尺。据信当时叙利亚战机正在附近打击叙利亚反对派武装。这次越境攻击事件使得黎巴嫩总统迈克尔·苏莱曼下令发起调查，但没有公开指责这起越境攻击事件<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2012/09/18/syrian-jets-hit-lebanese-territory-near-border/#ixzz27JvfB9lg|title=Syrian jets hit Lebanese territory near border|publisher=Fox News Channel|date=2012-09-18|accessdate=2012-12-25|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924181746/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2012/09/18/syrian-jets-hit-lebanese-territory-near-border/#ixzz27JvfB9lg|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

9月22日一伙叙利亚自由军攻击了对Arsal附近的一处边境哨所，据报道这是一周之内第二次越境袭击事件，武装分子被黎巴嫩政府军赶到了山区。黎巴嫩政府军扣押了这些武装分子，但稍后在当地头面人物的压力下释放了其中的一些人。黎巴嫩总统苏莱曼赞扬了政府军的行动，称其维护了黎巴嫩在外部冲突中的中立地位。他呼吁边境周围的居民拥护政府军并提供帮助。叙利亚政府再次呼吁黎巴嫩加大针对躲藏在黎巴嫩边境地区的叙利亚反对派的打击力道<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Sep-23/188927-lebanese-president-praises-army-response-to-fsa-attack.ashx#ixzz27JxWSuyo |title=Lebanese president praises Army response to FSA attack |work=The Daily Star |date=2012-09-23 |accessdate=2012-12-25 |archive-date=2020-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200209185355/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Sep-23/188927-lebanese-president-praises-army-response-to-fsa-attack.ashx#ixzz27JxWSuyo |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://cnnespanol.cnn.com/2012/09/22/rebeldes-sirios-atacan-un-puesto-del-ejercito-en-territorio-de-libano/|title=Rebeldes sirios atacan un puesto del Ejército en territorio de Líbano|author=Alkhshali Hamdi, Amir Ahmed, Mohammed Tawfeeq, Ben Brumfield and Joe Sterling|publisher=CNN Espanol|date=2012-09-22|accessdate=2012-12-25|archive-date=2012-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120928234910/http://cnnespanol.cnn.com/2012/09/22/rebeldes-sirios-atacan-un-puesto-del-ejercito-en-territorio-de-libano/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

10月11日四枚叙利亚政府军的炮弹落入了黎巴嫩城镇Masharih al-Qaa，该地区早先已经由于越境炮弹导致过人员伤亡。但黎巴嫩政府对越境攻击行为的无视态度以及竭力保证不卷入叙利亚内战的态度依旧未变。联合国的报告显示大约8万名来自叙利亚的难民如今正居住在黎巴嫩境内<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Oct-11/191029-syrian-shells-hit-lebanon-border-town.ashx#axzz28x8cZ38U|title=Syrian shells hit Lebanon border town|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-10-11|accessdate=2012-12-25|archive-date=2018-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181020081339/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Oct-11/191029-syrian-shells-hit-lebanon-border-town.ashx#axzz28x8cZ38U|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在10月黎巴嫩真主党领袖纳斯鲁拉否认真主党成员与叙利亚政府军并肩作战，但声称在叙利亚境内的黎巴嫩人只是在保卫黎巴嫩人居住的村庄免受叙利亚自由军的袭击<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/57430-report-5-000-pro-hizbullah-fighters-defending-lebanese-inhabited-border-towns-in-syria|title=Report: 5,000 Pro-Hizbullah Fighters Defending Lebanese-Inhabited Border Towns in Syria|publisher=Naharnet|accessdate=2012-10-20|archive-date=2019-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611122241/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/57430-report-5-000-pro-hizbullah-fighters-defending-lebanese-inhabited-border-towns-in-syria|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===2012年6月发生在难民营的冲突===

2012年6月16日在巴里德河难民营，1名巴勒斯坦人在与黎巴嫩政府军的冲突中丧生、8人受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/06/16/a-palestinian-killed-in-clashes-with-lebanese-army/|title=A Palestinian killed in clashes with Lebanese army|publisher=Ya Libnan|date=2012-06-06|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2019-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606004533/http://yalibnan.com/2012/06/16/a-palestinian-killed-in-clashes-with-lebanese-army/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月18日在针对黎巴嫩政府军的抗议活动中，兩名巴勒斯坦人在巴里德河难民营丧生、超过10人受伤。在Ain al-Hilweh的活动则导致1名巴勒斯坦人丧生<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Jun-19/177311-three-palestinians-killed-in-clashes-with-army.ashx#axzz1y8xjXkuw|title=Three Palestinians killed in clashes with Army|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-06-19|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2019-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190601135146/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Jun-19/177311-three-palestinians-killed-in-clashes-with-army.ashx#axzz1y8xjXkuw|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/palestinian-killed-lebanese-army-fire-northern-camp|title=Palestinian killed by Lebanese army in northern camp|publisher=Al Akhbar|date=2012-06-18|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130729183932/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/palestinian-killed-lebanese-army-fire-northern-camp|archive-date=2013-07-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。6月27日在Bourj al-Barajneh发生了冲突，但没有人员伤亡<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/44778-clash-involving-lebanese-families-palestinian-elements-in-bourj-al-barajneh|title=Clash Involving Lebanese Families, Palestinian Elements in Bourj al-Barajneh|publisher=Naharnet|date=2012-06-27|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605151344/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/44778-clash-involving-lebanese-families-palestinian-elements-in-bourj-al-barajneh|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

