逊尼派神职人员沙伊克·艾哈迈德·阿塞尔（Sheikh Ahmed Al-Assir）及其支持者在黎巴嫩南部城市[[赛达|赛达]]发起一场静坐示威活动，以抗议黎巴嫩真主党对叙利亚政府的支持<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jul-17/180860-assir-sit-in-raises-tension-in-south-as-preacher-awaits-dialogue.ashx#axzz21opU1zuW|title=Assir sit-in raises tension in south as preacher awaits Dialogue|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-07-17|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609055248/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jul-17/180860-assir-sit-in-raises-tension-in-south-as-preacher-awaits-dialogue.ashx#axzz21opU1zuW|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这使得局势变得紧张，之后还发生了阿塞尔的支持者和纳赛尔人民组织（Popular Nasserist Organization）之间的冲突<ref name="naharnet2">{{cite web|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/47986-rival-protests-leave-sidon-in-limbo|title=Bahia Hariri Says Seeking Pacification in Sidon after Rival Demos, Unrest|publisher=Naharnet|date=2012-07-27|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2019-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602200500/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/47986-rival-protests-leave-sidon-in-limbo|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jul-27/182239-scuffle-at-south-lebanon-sit-in-two-men-beaten.ashx#axzz21opU1zuW|title=Scuffle at south Lebanon sit-in, two men roughed up|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-07-27|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609010549/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jul-27/182239-scuffle-at-south-lebanon-sit-in-two-men-beaten.ashx#axzz21opU1zuW|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一名法新社的摄像师在冲突中受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/47919-afp-photographer-beaten-in-clash-between-asir-supporters-passersby|title=AFP Photographer Beaten in Clash between Asir Supporters, Passersby|publisher=Naharnet|date=2012-07-26|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609055333/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/47919-afp-photographer-beaten-in-clash-between-asir-supporters-passersby|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在第二天，赛达市举行了与阿塞尔的示威相对的示威活动。

8月8日阿塞尔的支持者与反对者之间发生枪战，导致5人受伤，其中包括两名妇女<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Aug-09/183935-gunfight-in-sidon-between-assir-and-local-rivals-wounds-five.ashx#axzz234YADSXf|title=Gunfight in Sidon between Assir and local rivals wounds five|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-08-09|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2012-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120823010227/http://dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Aug-09/183935-gunfight-in-sidon-between-assir-and-local-rivals-wounds-five.ashx#axzz234YADSXf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===米歇尔·萨马哈被捕事件===

2012年8月9日黎巴嫩警方拘捕了前黎巴嫩新闻部长米歇尔·萨马哈，之后此人被指控试图建立一支武装组织，在黎巴嫩为叙利亚政府代言，通发动恐怖袭击来煽动宗派暴力冲突。法庭还同时指控两名叙利亚军官，一名是叙利亚国家安全局领导人阿里·马穆鲁克（Ali Mamlouk）少将，另一名是阿德南准将。据报道，米歇尔·萨马哈承认计划对Akkar区及其他黎巴嫩北部目标发动炸弹袭击事件。反对叙利亚政府的“3月14日联盟”要求尽快调查这一事件，并且一旦证实，应该立即中断与叙利亚的外交关系，并且指控米歇尔·萨马哈叛国。支持叙利亚政府的“3月8日联盟”则指责萨马哈被捕事件是“3月14日联盟”的阴谋<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/08/12/samahas-bombing-plan-outrages-the-lebanese/|title=Samaha’s bombing plan outrages the Lebanese|publisher=Ya Libnan|date=2012-08-12|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2016-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160504120844/http://yalibnan.com/2012/08/12/samahas-bombing-plan-outrages-the-lebanese/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/49762-opposition-officials-demand-cutting-relations-with-syria-over-samaha-case|title=Opposition Officials Demand Cutting Relations with Syria over Samaha Case|publisher=Naharnet|date=2012-08-12|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2019-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190601135148/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/49762-opposition-officials-demand-cutting-relations-with-syria-over-samaha-case|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Nicholas Blanford|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Middle-East/2012/0810/Former-Lebanese-minister-arrested-for-planning-attacks-for-Syria-s-Assad|title=Former Lebanese minister arrested for planning attacks for Syria's Assad|work=The Christian Science Monitor|date=2012-08-10|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304035217/http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Middle-East/2012/0810/Former-Lebanese-minister-arrested-for-planning-attacks-for-Syria-s-Assad|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===的黎波里8月份冲突===

2012年8月9日来自Tawheed运动的支持真主党的逊尼派人士与萨拉菲主义者在的黎波里发生冲突<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Aug-14/184593-armed-clashes-increasing-in-frequency-in-tripoli.ashx#axzz29lXMXlNt|title=Armed clashes increasing in frequency in Tripoli|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-08-14|accessdate=2012-10-20|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605043127/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Politics/2012/Aug-14/184593-armed-clashes-increasing-in-frequency-in-tripoli.ashx#axzz29lXMXlNt|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="dailystar5">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Aug-09/183932-hezbollah-ally-camps-out-in-mosque-after-tripoli-clashes.ashx#axzz234YADSXf|title=Hezbollah ally camps out in mosque after Tripoli clashes|work=The Daily Star|date=2012-08-09|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116093912/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Aug-09/183932-hezbollah-ally-camps-out-in-mosque-after-tripoli-clashes.ashx#axzz234YADSXf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

8月20日至21日根据黎巴嫩安全部队和医疗机构的消息，在的黎波里逊尼派穆斯林与阿拉维派的冲突导致12人丧生、超过100人受伤，其中包括15名政府军士兵。至少有两名死者来自贾巴穆森社区，5人来自巴布艾特巴尼。在死者中有一名年仅13岁的男孩。在政府军受伤人员中有5人是在8月20日的枪战中受伤，还有5人是在次日一起针对一处政府军检查站的手榴弹袭击事件中受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mwcnews.net/news/middle-east/21016-lebanese-rivals.html|title=Lebanese rivals continue battles over Syria|publisher=Mwcnews|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2015-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151025031505/http://mwcnews.net/news/middle-east/21016-lebanese-rivals.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/08/21/us-lebanon-tripoli-idUSBRE87K0FC20120821|title=Fighting in Lebanese city for second night, 7 killed|agency=Reuters|date=2012-08-21|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2012-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120825064410/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/08/21/us-lebanon-tripoli-idUSBRE87K0FC20120821|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

8月22日黎巴嫩政府军再次尝试阻止暴力冲突发生。政府军向长期有冲突的社区派遣了部队。但是，政府军遭遇严重损失，并被迫撤退。在与社区领导人进行对话后，政府军成功使得冲突双方达成停火<ref name=BBCAugust23>{{cite news|title=Lebanon clashes: Fresh clashes breach truce in Tripoli|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-19354337|accessdate=2012-08-23|publisher=BBC News|date=2012-08-23|archive-date=2012-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120823141627/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-19354337|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

但停火在8月23日以失败告终，在全城范围内爆发了新的一系列冲突。黎巴嫩政府军向街道内部署了坦克以试图再次控制局势<ref name=BBCAugust23/>。

8月24日在当天黎明Qobbah和 Jabal Muhsin街区逊尼派和阿拉维派武装分子使用轻武器和火箭弹展开交火，逊尼派神职人员Sheikh Khaled al Barade在冲突中被狙击手枪杀。据报道Sheikh Khaled al Barade是一伙逊尼派伊斯兰武装分子的首领，他的死导致城内发生新的教派骚乱，战斗也因此进一步升级。在逊尼派社区至少有7座阿拉维派群众的商铺遭到不明身份的袭击者焚毁，在持续一天的战斗中有两名新闻记者受伤<ref name=BBC24AugustClericKilled>{{cite news|title=Sunni cleric killed in north Lebanon clashes|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-19366256|accessdate=2012-08-24|date=2012-08-24|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2012-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120824113127/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-19366256|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

据统计这一轮冲突共导致17人丧生、超过120人受伤<ref>{{cite news|author=Mitchell Prothero|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/aug/25/lebanon-tripoli-turned-into-war-zone|title=Tripoli turned into a war zone as rivals fight street duels with grenades|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2012-08-26|accessdate=2012-10-20|location=London|archive-date=2012-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020212114/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/aug/25/lebanon-tripoli-turned-into-war-zone|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Aug-24/185571-clashes-erupt-anew-in-north-lebanon-after-sheikh-killed.ashx#axzz24ToAs8hU|title=Renewed north Lebanon clashes kill 3, including Salafist sheikh|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2012-08-21|accessdate=2012-08-25|archive-date=2016-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413225826/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Aug-24/185571-clashes-erupt-anew-in-north-lebanon-after-sheikh-killed.ashx#axzz24ToAs8hU|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===维萨姆·哈桑遇刺事件===

2012年10月19日在贝鲁特Achrafiyeh社区发生一起汽车炸弹袭击事件，造成8人丧生，其中包括黎巴嫩安全部队情报局长维萨姆·哈桑准将，爆炸袭击事件还造成另外78人受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/57713-wissam-al-hasan-assassinated-in-ashrafiyeh-bomb-blast|title=Wissam al-Hasan Assassinated in Ashrafiyeh Bomb Blast|publisher=Naharnet|accessdate=2012-10-20|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117022149/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/57713-wissam-al-hasan-assassinated-in-ashrafiyeh-bomb-blast|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这起爆炸事件是自2008年以来发生在贝鲁特的最为严重的一起袭击事件<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/57701-8-dead-78-hurt-as-powerful-car-bomb-hits-near-ashrafiyeh-s-sassine-square|title=8 Dead, 78 Hurt as Powerful Car Bomb Hits near Ashrafiyeh's Sassine Square|publisher=Naharnet|accessdate=2012-10-20|archive-date=2018-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005215706/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/57701-8-dead-78-hurt-as-powerful-car-bomb-hits-near-ashrafiyeh-s-sassine-square|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于维萨姆·哈桑被认为与反阿萨德阵营关系密切，所以很快有人怀疑叙利亚政府或其盟友策划了这起袭击事件。维萨姆·哈桑主导着一项调查牵扯到叙利亚及其盟友黎巴嫩真主党卷入了前总理拉菲克·哈里里遇刺事件<ref>{{cite news |author=Mitchell Prothero and Peter Beaumont |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/oct/19/beirut-car-bomb-kills-8 |title=Anti-Syrian security official among dead in Beirut car bomb attack |work=The Guardian |date=2012-10-19 |accessdate=2012-12-25 |location=London |archive-date=2012-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121118001804/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/oct/19/beirut-car-bomb-kills-8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但是在调查过程中维萨姆·哈桑本人也是哈里里背刺案的主要嫌疑人，因为他与沙特情报部门关系密切，据称与[[摩萨德|摩萨德]]也有联系<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.spiegel.de/international/world/lebanon-tribunal-may-investigate-recent-assassination-a-865242.html|title=Lebanon Tribunal May Investigate Recent Assassination|work=Der Spiegel|accessdate=2012-11-27|journal=|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010115058/http://www.spiegel.de/international/world/lebanon-tribunal-may-investigate-recent-assassination-a-865242.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

这次暗杀事件在黎巴嫩全国都引发了骚乱事件<ref>{{cite web|author=benzona|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/57719-roads-blocked-across-lebanon-in-protest-at-al-hasan-assassination|title=Roads Blocked across Lebanon in Protest at al-Hasan Assassination|publisher=Naharnet|accessdate=2012-10-20|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605151343/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/57719-roads-blocked-across-lebanon-in-protest-at-al-hasan-assassination|dead-url=no}}</ref>。黎巴嫩未来电视台的一名主持人号召了人群前往黎巴嫩议会总部，最终导致抗议示威者与警察发生冲突<ref>{{cite paper|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=449326|title=Journalist says his Serail call not coordinated with March 14|publisher=NOW Lebanon|accessdate=2012-10-24|journal=|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025114021/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=449326|archive-date=2012-10-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。逊尼派武装分子设立检查站，仔细盘查过路人的宗派隶属关系<ref>{{cite paper|last=Sherlock|first=Ruth|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/lebanon/9626276/Lebanon-fate-of-the-nation-at-stake.html|title=Lebanon: 'fate of the nation at stake'|work=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2012-10-24|journal=|archive-date=2012-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023174621/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/lebanon/9626276/Lebanon-fate-of-the-nation-at-stake.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在维萨姆·哈萨死后，[[萨阿德·哈里里|萨阿德·哈里里]]及一些来自反对叙利亚政府的“3月14日联盟”的政治领袖直接指责叙利亚策划了这起袭击事件<ref name="BBC-profile">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-20004476|title=Profile: Wissam al-Hassan|date=2012-10-19|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2012-10-19|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202100452/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-20004476|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

10月21日由暗杀所引发的暴力冲突在全国范围内发生。在贾巴穆森与巴布艾特巴尼两个社区间的冲突中两名小女孩和1名男子丧生<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Oct-22/192271-three-dead-in-tripoli-clashes-arrests-made.ashx#axzz29z9qZY9N|title=Three dead in Tripoli clashes, arrests made|work=The Daily Star|accessdate=2012-10-23|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116091332/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Oct-22/192271-three-dead-in-tripoli-clashes-arrests-made.ashx#axzz29z9qZY9N|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当天晚上，在贝鲁特Tariq al-Jadeedah社区前总理哈里里的拥护者与敌对派别发生冲突<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/57902-cautious-calm-in-tariq-al-jadeedah-after-overnight-clashes|title=Army Carrying Out Security Plan in Beirut to Detain Gunmen, Restore Order|publisher=Naharnet|accessdate=2012-10-23|archive-date=2017-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170708000823/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/57902-cautious-calm-in-tariq-al-jadeedah-after-overnight-clashes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月22日在的黎波里，兩名逊尼派和1名阿拉维派在冲突中丧生、另有15人受伤。从10月19日到23日的冲突总计造成13人丧生、65人受伤<ref>{{cite news|last=Holmes|first=Oliver|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/10/23/us-lebanon-crisis-idUSBRE89L0CK20121023|title=Fighting flares in Lebanese city over Syria loyalties|agency=Reuters|date=2012-10-23|accessdate=2012-10-23|archive-date=2012-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023234225/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/10/23/us-lebanon-crisis-idUSBRE89L0CK20121023|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

10月24日未来阵线的抗议者与黎巴嫩政府军发生冲突<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/58329-march-14-protesters-clash-with-security-forces-in-riad-al-solh|title=March 14 Protesters Clash with Security Forces in Riad al-Solh|publisher=Naharnet|date=2012-10-25|accessdate=2012-11-27|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603194719/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/58329-march-14-protesters-clash-with-security-forces-in-riad-al-solh|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===赛达市冲突===

