12月2日，黎巴嫩政府军与叙利亚反对派在叙黎边境附近发生冲突，冲突没有造成人员伤亡。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/63080-lebanese-army-clashes-with-syrian-rebels-on-bekaa-border |title=Lebanese Army Clashes with Syrian Rebels on Bekaa Border |publisher=Naharnet.com |date=2012-12-02 |accessdate=2012-12-24 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215322/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/63080-lebanese-army-clashes-with-syrian-rebels-on-bekaa-border |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2012年12月4日至9日，在的黎波里的冲突至少造成19人丧生，超过140人受伤。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/Flash.aspx/257031#.UMT0goP7JCg|title=Syrian-Related Death Toll in Tripoli Rises to Six|publisher=Arutz Sheva|date=2012-12-09|accessdate=2012-12-25|archive-date=2017-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904204928/http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/Flash.aspx/257031#.UMT0goP7JCg|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/world/report_lebanon-s-tripoli-begins-to-look-like-syria_1774766|title=Lebanon's Tripoli begins to look like Syria|publisher=Dna India|date=2012-12-07|accessdate=2012-12-25}}</ref>这起冲突是由之前Tall Kalakh伏击所引发的，冲突双方为阿拉维派和逊尼派。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/12/2012124152513238762.html |title=Fatal sectarian clashes in Lebanon’s Tripoli |publisher=Al Jazeera |date=2012-12-04 |accessdate=2012-12-25 |archive-date=2018-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002214746/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/12/2012124152513238762.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/12/2012125145553286195.html |title=Deadly clashes in Lebanon's Tripoli |publisher=Al Jazeera |accessdate=2012-12-25 |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402114120/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/12/2012125145553286195.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/63688-army-units-continue-to-deploy-in-tripoli-after-worst-night-in-fighting-in-years |title=Army Units Deploy in Tripoli as Clashes, Sniper Fire Renew at Night |publisher=Naharnet |date=2012-12-07 |accessdate=2012-12-24 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608213936/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/63688-army-units-continue-to-deploy-in-tripoli-after-worst-night-in-fighting-in-years |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/63506-report-lebanese-men-arrested-in-tall-kalakh-to-be-tried-in-damascus |title=Report: Lebanese Men Arrested in Tall Kalakh to Be Tried in Damascus |publisher=Naharnet |date=2012-12-06 |accessdate=2012-12-24 |archive-date=2019-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603092552/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/63506-report-lebanese-men-arrested-in-tall-kalakh-to-be-tried-in-damascus |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.trust.org/alertnet/news/three-killed-by-snipers-in-sectarian-clashes-in-lebanons-tripoli/ |title=Three killed by snipers in sectarian clashes in Lebanon's Tripoli |publisher=Trust.org |date=2012-12-06 |accessdate=2012-12-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130415235022/http://www.trust.org/alertnet/news/three-killed-by-snipers-in-sectarian-clashes-in-lebanons-tripoli/ |archivedate=2013-04-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/63545-sniper-activity-clashes-renew-in-tripoli-as-death-toll-reach-11 |title=Sniper Activity, Clashes Renew in Tripoli as Death Toll Reaches 11 |publisher=Naharnet |date=2012-12-06 |accessdate=2012-12-24 |archive-date=2019-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605043114/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/63545-sniper-activity-clashes-renew-in-tripoli-as-death-toll-reach-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

