===费萨尔·卡拉米车队遇袭事件===

2013年1月18日，黎巴嫩青年与体育部长费萨尔·卡拉米的车队在的黎波里遭遇示威者攻击。当时一群示威者正在举行静坐活动，要求释放被关押的恐怖组织“伊斯兰法塔赫”的成员。在事件中有5人受伤。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/68828-five-injured-as-minister-karami-s-convoy-comes-under-attack |title=5 Injured in Attack against Minister Karami's Convoy as Ex-PM Omar Karami Laments Lack of Security in Lebanon |publisher=Naharnet.com |date=2013-01-18 |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608111138/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/68828-five-injured-as-minister-karami-s-convoy-comes-under-attack |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===Arsal冲突===

