d-in-tripoli-clashes |title=Five soldiers injured in Tripoli clashes |publisher=Now.mmedia.me |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305030358/https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/lebanonnews/five-soldiers-injured-in-tripoli-clashes |dead-url=no }}</ref>贾巴穆森社区遭到政府军的搜查，而阿拉伯民主党领导人Rifa'at Eid则对此表示怀疑，因为敌对的巴布艾特巴尼社区并没有遭到突击搜查。<ref>[http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/85631-army-starts-removing-jabal-mohsen-barricades-eid-voices-reservation-and-kabbara-gives-48-hour-ultimatum Army Starts Removing Jabal Mohsen Barricades, Eid Voices Reservation and Kabbara Gives 48-Hour Ultimatum — Naharnet] {{Wayback|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/85631-army-starts-removing-jabal-mohsen-barricades-eid-voices-reservation-and-kabbara-gives-48-hour-ultimatum |date=20181221200709 }}. Naharnet.com (2013-06-04). Retrieved on 2013-10-29.</ref>

