===第三次Arsal冲突===

2013年6月12日，据报道1架叙利亚陆军直升机向Arsal发射了三枚火箭弹。该镇距离叙黎边境15公里。一枚火箭弹击中了小镇中心，导致人员受伤。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22870776 |title=Syria rebels 'kill Shia residents of eastern village' 12 June 2013 |publisher=BBC |date=2013-06-12 |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312013254/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22870776 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

