===穆罕默德·沙塔赫遇刺事件===

2013年12月27日大约9:40，<ref name="blame">{{cite news |date=2013-12-27 |title=Lebanon: Hezbollah critic Mohamad Chatah’s murder blamed on Shia militant movement |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/beirut-bomb-blast-kills-six-including-antiassad-exminister-9027038.html |newspaper=The Independent |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223170450/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/beirut-bomb-blast-kills-six-including-antiassad-exminister-9027038.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在贝鲁特市中心，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-25524729|title=Beirut blast kills Sunni ex-minister Mohamad Chatah|date=2013-12-27|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|accessdate=2014-03-02|archive-date=2013-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227171712/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-25524729|dead-url=no}}</ref>一起汽车炸弹袭击了穆罕默德·沙塔赫的车队，造成包括沙塔赫在内的8人丧生，70人受伤。<ref name="deathtoll">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Lebanon-News/2013/Dec-29/242571-beirut-bombing-death-toll-rises-to-eight.ashx#axzz2ouh2KRqT|title=Beirut bombing death toll rises to eight|date=2013-12-29|website=|publisher=''[[The_Daily_Star_(Lebanon)|The Daily Star]]''|accessdate=2014-03-02|archive-date=2018-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181117035642/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Lebanon-News/2013/Dec-29/242571-beirut-bombing-death-toll-rises-to-eight.ashx#axzz2ouh2KRqT|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name="cnn">{{cite web|url=http://cnn.com/2013/12/27/world/meast/lebanon-explosion/|title=Lebanon's Chatah -- friend of U.S., enemy of Assad, Hezbollah -- killed|date=2013-12-27|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|accessdate=2014-03-02|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608111146/https://www.cnn.com/2013/12/27/world/meast/lebanon-explosion/|dead-url=no}}</ref>穆罕默德·沙塔赫是前黎巴嫩经济部长和驻美大使。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/mohamad-chatah-lebanese-ex-minister-killed-in-beirut-bombing-1.2476861|title=Mohamad Chatah, Lebanese ex-minister, killed in Beirut bombing|date=2013-12-27|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|accessdate=2014-03-02|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012115938/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/mohamad-chatah-lebanese-ex-minister-killed-in-beirut-bombing-1.2476861|dead-url=no}}</ref>据估计袭击所使用的炸药重达50公斤，被安置在一辆失窃的本田车中。<ref name="blame"/>这起袭击被认为是针对沙塔赫的带有政治目的的暗杀事件。<ref name="reuters">{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/27/us-syria-crisis-beirut-bomb-idUSBRE9BQ01H20131227|title=Beirut bomb kills Lebanese ex-minister who opposed Assad|date=2013-12-27|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|accessdate=2014-03-02|archive-date=2014-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140213053854/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/27/us-syria-crisis-beirut-bomb-idUSBRE9BQ01H20131227|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

===2012年1月2日贝鲁特炸弹袭击事件===

2012年1月2日，在贝鲁特Haret Hreik区（该地区被认为是真主党的重要活动区域）发生一起汽车炸弹袭击事件，造成至少5人丧生。这起炸弹袭击事件发生在一座被真主党的Al-Manar电视台使用的建筑物外，并且靠近附近被真主党所有的办公建筑。<ref>"Beirut blast kills at least five in Hezbollah stronghold." BBC News. January 2, 2014. Accessed January 13, 2014.  http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-25577642 {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-25577642 |date=20140220035109 }}</ref>

===2014年1月16日赫尔梅尔炸弹袭击事件===

2014年1月16日，一名自杀式爆炸袭击者在赫尔梅尔市的真主党据点外引爆了汽车炸弹。至少3人在袭击事件中丧生，其中也包括自杀式袭击者，另外还造成26人受伤。<ref>Dziadosz, Alexander. "Lebanon car bomb kills four in Hezbollah stronghold near Syria." Reuters. Jan. 16, 2014. Accessed Jan. 16, 2014. http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/01/16/us-lebanon-bomb-idUSBREA0F0AJ20140116 {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/01/16/us-lebanon-bomb-idUSBREA0F0AJ20140116 |date=20150930210644 }}</ref>

===2014年1月17日火箭弹袭击事件===

2014年1月17日，在发生汽车炸弹袭击事件1天后，数枚火箭弹击中了赫尔梅尔市，没有造成人员伤亡。另一枚火箭弹击中Arsal镇，导致7人丧生，15人受伤。<ref>[http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/01/17/us-lebanon-syria-rocket-idUSBREA0G0IX20140117 Rocket fired from Syria kills seven in Lebanese border town] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/01/17/us-lebanon-syria-rocket-idUSBREA0G0IX20140117 |date=20150924192606 }}, Reuters, Rami Bleibel, January 17, 2014</ref>

