==国内反应==
叙利亚内战及其国际影响使得黎巴嫩政坛进一步两极分化。基督教政党和逊尼派政党主导的政治联盟“3月14日联盟”普遍同情叙利亚反对派。2012年8月，隶属于“3月14日联盟”的黎巴嫩长枪党、黎巴嫩力量党、未来阵线的年轻成员组织了一场集会，要求将叙利亚大使驱逐出境。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/51597-march-14-student-bodies-rally-at-foreign-ministry-to-demand-syrian-ambassador-s-expulsion|title=March 14 starts campaign to expel Syrian envoy|newspaper=Naharnet|date=2012-08-30|accessdate=2014-03-02|archive-date=2012-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120830184338/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/51597-march-14-student-bodies-rally-at-foreign-ministry-to-demand-syrian-ambassador-s-expulsion|dead-url=no}}</ref>

“3月8日联盟”普遍支持叙利亚政府，但分析人士相信联盟内的一些党派正在试图寻找如果阿萨德政权倒台后的新盟友。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=432512&MID=0&PID=0|title=The future of Syria’s pawns in Lebanon|newspaper=NOW Lebanon|date=2012-09-02|access-date=2014-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120904110027/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=432512&MID=0&PID=0|archive-date=2012-09-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>政府内一些温和派成员已经开始与阿萨德政权保持距离。而先前与阿萨德政权结盟的Walid Jumblatt的“社会进步党”已经转变立场反对阿萨德政权。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/51729-psp-to-rally-in-support-of-syrian-people-expulsion-of-syrian-ambassador|title=PSP to Rally in Support of Syrian People, Expulsion of Syrian Ambassador|deadurl=no|accessdate=2012-09-03|archive-date=2018-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181006004400/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/51729-psp-to-rally-in-support-of-syrian-people-expulsion-of-syrian-ambassador}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/51973-psp-demo-urges-syria-envoy-expulsion-arrest-of-syrians-in-samaha-case|title=PSP Demo Urges Syria Envoy Expulsion, Arrest of Syrians in Samaha Case|deadurl=no|accessdate=3012-09-03|archive-date=2012-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120902194126/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/51973-psp-demo-urges-syria-envoy-expulsion-arrest-of-syrians-in-samaha-case}}</ref>

截止2013年2月13日，在黎巴嫩已经有超过18万叙利亚难民。<ref>{{cite web|title=Demographic Data of Registered Population|url=http://data.unhcr.org/syrianrefugees/regional.php|publisher=UNHCR|accessdate=2013-02-14|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225193400/https://data2.unhcr.org/en/situations/syria|dead-url=no}}</ref>随着叙利亚难民日趋增多，黎巴嫩力量党、[[黎巴嫩长枪党|黎巴嫩长枪党]]和自由爱国运动<ref>{{cite web|last=Kverme|first=Kai|title=The Refugee Factor|url=http://carnegieendowment.org/2013/02/14/refugee-factor/fgl0|publisher=SADA|accessdate=2013-02-14|date=2013-02-14|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029192335/http://carnegieendowment.org/2013/02/14/refugee-factor/fgl0|dead-url=yes}}</ref>担心黎巴嫩的政治格局将会被侵蚀。

